{"original_text": "//@昕飞扬1996: “上大学，就是要选点儿以后在社会上听不到的课。大学，不是蓝翔技所，我们学习，不仅仅是去学一门拿来用的手艺。”", "evtlist": [423], "uid": "1985499101", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "", "tr": 22, "mid": "3619323648083212", "times": 1, "childnum": 5, "t": 1378397461, "totalChildren": 22, "dr": 5, "children": [{"evtlist": [423], "uid": "1180765975", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3619323648083212", "tr": 0, "mid": "3619324608403477", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1378397693, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "晋博Krist"}, {"evtlist": [423], "uid": "1718938111", "dep": 0, "text": "“上大学，就是要选点儿以后在社会上听不到的课。大学，不是蓝翔技所，我们学习，不仅仅是去学一门拿来用的手艺。”", "pid": "3619323648083212", "tr": 16, "mid": "3619328203534704", "times": 1, "childnum": 2, "t": 1378398548, "totalChildren": 16, "dr": 2, "children": [{"evtlist": [423], "uid": "1802131451", "dep": 0, "text": " ", "pid": "3619328203534704", "tr": 0, "mid": "3619329742834335", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1378398916, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "子瑛180"}, {"evtlist": [423], "uid": "1794892070", "dep": 0, "text": "能意识到这一点的通常都是优秀学生 [哈哈]", "pid": "3619328203534704", "tr": 14, "mid": "3619357571225447", "times": 1, "childnum": 5, "t": 1378405555, "totalChildren": 14, "dr": 5, "children": [{"evtlist": [423], "uid": "1748058361", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3619357571225447", "tr": 0, "mid": "3619360508040456", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1378406252, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "三个洞"}, {"evtlist": [423], "uid": "1776281393", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3619357571225447", "tr": 0, "mid": "3619360746692818", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1378406309, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "EdlinLink_俊豪"}, {"evtlist": [423], "uid": "1649518534", "dep": 0, "text": "公选课，当然选非本专业的兴趣所在，尤其中大这种学科齐全的综合性大学提供了多样化的选择，不容错过啊", "pid": "3619357571225447", "tr": 0, "mid": "3619436437635374", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1378424355, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "molee小茉莉"}, {"evtlist": [423], "uid": "1769220371", "dep": 0, "text": "昨天保研面试，兄弟学院某女老师说，你院不是向来学风严谨的吗，怎么基本的问题好多学生都答忘了；现在连温和的@错别字达人 都说大三技能课太多，学生喜技能，而不是喜欢基本理论；还有法师说，大三好多课没必要开，俺的课则应变为全院专选，要求接受他方向的学生上课。。。[哈哈]", "pid": "3619357571225447", "tr": 6, "mid": "3619444582127064", "times": 1, "childnum": 1, "t": 1378426296, "totalChildren": 6, "dr": 1, "children": [{"evtlist": [423], "uid": "1794892070", "dep": 0, "text": "还是那句话：一流大学最终拼的是基础。", "pid": "3619444582127064", "tr": 5, "mid": "3619487788060430", "times": 1, "childnum": 3, "t": 1378436598, "totalChildren": 5, "dr": 3, "children": [{"evtlist": [423], "uid": "2212452253", "dep": 0, "text": " ", "pid": "3619487788060430", "tr": 1, "mid": "3619488153046340", "times": 1, "childnum": 1, "t": 1378436684, "totalChildren": 1, "dr": 1, "children": [{"evtlist": [423], "uid": "1595557625", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3619488153046340", "tr": 0, "mid": "3619494603677181", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1378438223, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "小莱豆_00"}], "name": "陈振宇NJU"}, {"evtlist": [423], "uid": "1769220371", "dep": 0, "text": "以一流生源拼技能，类似田忌赛马，就业率高自然不是奇怪事情，何况顶着先贤立下的名字；奇怪的是，不是很多学生能意识到自己进来称为大学的地方，没有在思维上增值多少，变成了高中四年级，五年级；没有了机会跟现实保持点距离，在一生中形而上一下", "pid": "3619487788060430", "tr": 1, "mid": "3619500362378498", "times": 1, "childnum": 1, "t": 1378439596, "totalChildren": 1, "dr": 1, "children": [{"evtlist": [423], "uid": "1794892070", "dep": 0, "text": "不要说学生, 有多少教师和管理者能意识到?", "pid": "3619500362378498", "tr": 0, "mid": "3619502615139802", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1378440132, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "西里村"}], "name": "JohnJoan"}, {"evtlist": [423], "uid": "2667026151", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3619487788060430", "tr": 0, "mid": "3619501347708822", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1378439830, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "站在山海之间"}], "name": "西里村"}], "name": "JohnJoan"}, {"evtlist": [423], "uid": "1794892070", "dep": 0, "text": "回复@molee小茉莉:大学期间选课除了兴趣还要注重其他方面。有些糊弄学生的技能课如如何使用Photoshop、Flash等不少学生感兴趣，但不是应该在一流大学里教的，是蓝翔技校的课程 ", "pid": "3619357571225447", "tr": 3, "mid": "3619447937789887", "times": 1, "childnum": 3, "t": 1378427096, "totalChildren": 3, "dr": 3, "children": [{"evtlist": [423], "uid": "1942482717", "dep": 0, "text": "那…手机应用开发呢…[疑问]", "pid": "3619447937789887", "tr": 0, "mid": "3619450660368097", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1378427746, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "何晓斌_粤语闻舞奔"}, {"evtlist": [423], "uid": "2048668647", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3619447937789887", "tr": 0, "mid": "3619462987224932", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1378430684, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "X_J_C_"}, {"evtlist": [423], "uid": "2381148182", "dep": 0, "text": "深表赞同！ ", "pid": "3619447937789887", "tr": 0, "mid": "3619476912044069", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1378434005, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "real孙立"}], "name": "西里村"}], "name": "西里村"}], "name": "视觉研究"}, {"evtlist": [423], "uid": "2627058773", "dep": 0, "text": "[鼓掌] ", "pid": "3619323648083212", "tr": 1, "mid": "3619333471480957", "times": 1, "childnum": 1, "t": 1378399803, "totalChildren": 1, "dr": 1, "children": [{"evtlist": [423], "uid": "2493642777", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3619333471480957", "tr": 0, "mid": "3619450919971527", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1378427810, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "Soardbj"}], "name": "谢磊NPU"}, {"evtlist": [423], "uid": "1792823117", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3619323648083212", "tr": 0, "mid": "3619472726177953", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1378433007, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "陆宁波"}, {"evtlist": [423], "uid": "1720066421", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3619323648083212", "tr": 0, "mid": "3619592855016269", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1378461648, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "QLUQ"}], "name": "晓如微博"}